---
title: Sweet-Soy Chicken & Chilli Jam Glaze with Carrot Salad & Crispy Shallots
description: This classic seasoning blend combines goes nicely with succulent chicken and paired with a sweet chilli sauce makes
a perfect match! Rest it on a cushy pillow of carrot salad to serve.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65ea492ebbb0ffe7102d1f17-64e7e656.jpeg
